{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fde73150a6","title":"转发华东军区党委关于打虎预算报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c469a6a49","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":30,"articleId":"fde73150a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"c992908ebe","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fde73150a6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共华东军区委员会1952年1月29日给各级党委和首长并报毛泽东、华东局的报告规定了华东各部队打虎的预算，预计华东部队在打虎阶段总共要打出大老虎266个，小老虎865个，中小贪污分子86850人。"}],"contents":[{"id":"35eccf7a94","type":"title","text":"转发华东军区党委关于打虎预算报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fde73150a6"},{"id":"c992908ebe","type":"paragraph","text":"各大军区，志愿军，并客中央局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fde73150a6"},{"id":"f1b1d1dd24","type":"paragraph","text":"华东军区一月二十九日规定打虎预算的精神很好，发给你介参考。一个大军区不会只有两百多个大老虎，但第一次规定这样一个数目是适当的，以后可以根据认识的深入逐步追加打虎任务。中央一级十二万人，清出贪污分子一万人（百分之八十以上是一百万元以下的小贪污分子，一般须从轻处理），已经清出或准备清出的大老虎四百只，这是经过多次严格督促、不断追加任务才达成的奋斗目标。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fde73150a6"},{"id":"61a41f7ae3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fde73150a6"},{"id":"a586d4d4a9","type":"paragraph","text":"一月三十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fde73150a6"}],"page":{"id":"0f50fca061","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fde73150a6","start":312,"end":312}}}},"__N_SSG":true}